<HEADLINE> People's Daily Editorial Stresses Economic Development (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"The great shift is also the fundamental reason for the rapid
development of our country and the remarkable improvement of our
people's lives," the editorial adds.
</P>
<P>
Therefore, it says, taking economic development as the central
task all the time is the key to the resolution of all problems
China now faces.
</P>
<P>
"We must focus on economic development while handling both
domestic and international issues. Even if we're involved in a
large-scale war, we must remember to go back to economic
development as soon as the war is over," it elaborates.
