He stressed that Chinese President Jiang Zemin has
comprehensively elaborated the solemn stand of the Chinese
government on the Kosovo issue and the case of the U.S.-led NATO
attack on Chinese embassy in Belgrade.
</P>
<P>
He went on to say that President Jiang Zemin and Russian
President Boris Yeltsin had talked by phone, and both denounced
NATO's brutal act and reached common ground on the settlement of
the Kosovo issue.
