<HEADLINE> Cathay Pacific Honored By Newspaper </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 24 (Xinhua) -- Cathay Pacific Airways got three
first place awards in the South China Morning Post/Post Magazine's
1999 travel awards, the airline said Monday.
</P>
<P>
The airline was voted "Best Business Class," "Best Economy
Class Entertainment" and "Most Child-Friendly Airline" in the Post
Magazine's first annual reader survey.
</P>
<P>
The airline, named "Best Airline-Business Class" at the 1999
Travel Trade Gazette Travel Awards in April, was also placed
second in four other categories from a total of eight major awards
for the airline industry.
</P>
<P>
More than 1,500 readers participated in the travel survey.
