<BODY>
<HEADLINE> French Open Tennis Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, May 24 (Xinhua) -- Following are the men's singles
results at the French Open tennis tournament on Monday (prefix
number denotes seeding)
</P>
<P>
First round :
</P>
<P>
4-Carlos Moya, Spain, bt Markus Hipfl, Austria, 3-6, 1-6, 6-4,
6-2, 6-4
</P>
<P>
Dominik Hrbaty, Slovakia, bt Julien Boutter, France, 5-7, 6-4,
7-5, 7-5
</P>
<P>
Hicham Arazi, Morocco, bt 15-Goran Ivanisevic, Croatia, 6-4, 1-
6, 6-3, 6-1
</P>
<P>
