of its Constitution, which came into force on May 23, 1949, in a
simple and modest way. The playing of the music by Mozart, Brahms
and Mendelssohn, as well as the national anthem, plus a short
speech by the president of the republic, will be all of the
ceremony.
</P>
<P>
