<HEADLINE> South Korea Reshuffles Cabinet (With Correction) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SEOUL, May 24 (Xinhua) -- South Korean President Kim Dae-jung
Monday announced a sweeping reshuffle of his cabinet, replacing 11
of the 17 cabinet members.
</P>
<P>
